nodes.text: Star Wars Jedi Quest CommLink Premier Issue

Star Wars Jedi Quest CommLink Premier Issue was the inaugural issue of Star Wars Jedi Quest Kids Club Magazine, originally titled Star Wars Jedi Quest CommLink. The magazine was released for Hasbro's Star Wars Jedi Quest Kids Club in April 2000. It was followed by two additional issues later that year. The magazine had seven pages on with information about upcoming action figures.
